  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And at that time, then I started my own investigation of trying to find out what happened.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were many things that happened in Dachau, obviously, that I did not know about because in a large area like that with all the buildings, it was-- my vision was always limited.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I knew that things had gone on there that I did not know about.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I wasn't sure what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I finally had a good friend who was an inspector general in the Army, a colonel, had retired.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And a few years ago, I asked him to see if he could dig out all the records that are available.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he knew his way around in Washington.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And anybody trying to find anything in the United States Archives with the hundreds of millions of documents, it's a daunting task.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He started it anyway and spent several days at that job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he discovered then and prepared for me the most complete record of Dachau that has ever been compiled, this huge book that he got records from archives.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there finally was the long missing investigation.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
